{"tid":1641412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雙十國慶 普天同慶","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:08:34.000Z","uid":284129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a2adab6259bb1facd8212eff1d99c3a4cc85c5","tid":1641412,"uid":284129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"中共最驚既唔係英國旗 美國旗 英國國歌 美國國歌<br />\n而係正統中國 中華民國嘅青天白日滿地紅旗同民國嘅國歌同國旗歌<br />\n中共絕對驚慌係自己管轄區出現民國旗 民眾唱民國國歌及國旗歌<br />\n因為佢好驚大陸民眾掀起民國熱<br />\n打住民國旗號去反佢呢個極權非法政府<br />\n🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼"},{"pid":"800b6935aeeafa2e3932d57d52685f2e1b1e359f","tid":1641412,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"紀念雙十，點少得十八星旗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641102</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/Lc77Tax.png\" />"}]}